tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MedicationAdherence (
  patient_id INT,
  medication_name VARCHAR(255),
  prescribed_dosage INT,
  actual_dosage INT,
  adherence_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE patients(
  patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  medication_name VARCHAR(50),
  medication_dosage INT,
  medication_schedule TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE adherence_data(
  adherence_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  adherence_date TIMESTAMPTZ,
  adherence_level INT,
  adherence_reason TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    medication_history VARCHAR(500)
);

CREATE TABLE Adherence (
    adherence_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    medication_id INT,
    date_adhered TIMESTAMP,
    adherence_percentage FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (medication_id) REFERENCES Medications(medication_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Compliance_Predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    medication_id INT,
    predicted_compliance FLOAT,
    prediction_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (medication_id) REFERENCES Medications(medication_id)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    insurance_id VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE prescriptions (
    prescription_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    med_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
